<body>
    <h1>Data Deletion Instructions for Crosswalk Wand</h1>
    <p><strong>App Name:</strong> Crosswalk Wand</p>
    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Crosswalk Wand helps people cross the road safely using audio and visual animation sequences displayed on their monitor.</p>
    
    <h2>Data Collected:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Email addresses</li>
        <li>Facebook usernames</li>
        <li>Gmail addresses</li>
        <li>Phone numbers</li>
        <li>Location data</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Storage:</h2>
    <p>All collected data is securely stored in the cloud using Firebase Firestore.</p>

    <h2>Data Usage:</h2>
    <p>The data collected by Crosswalk Wand is used to identify and analyze locations with the highest pedestrian crossings. This helps us improve our services and ensure user safety.</p>

    <h2>Data Deletion Process:</h2>
    <p>If you wish to delete your data from our system, please follow these steps:</p>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Compose an Email:</strong> Open your email application and create a new email.</li>
        <li><strong>Email Address:</strong> Address the email to <a href="mailto:cw@kiloin.app">cw@kiloin.app</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Subject Line:</strong> Set the subject line as "Data Deletion Request".</li>
        <li><strong>Email Body:</strong> In the body of the email, provide the following information to help us locate your data:
            <ul>
                <li>Your Facebook username</li>
                <li>The email address associated with your Crosswalk Wand account (this can be your email or Gmail address)</li>
                <li>Your phone number</li>
                <li>Your location (optional but helpful)</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Send the Email:</strong> Send the email to our support team.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Confirmation:</h2>
    <p>After receiving your request, our team will process it and confirm the deletion of your data within 30 days. You will receive a confirmation email once the data has been deleted.</p>

    <h2>Important Note:</h2>
    <p>Please be aware that deleting your data may result in the inability to access or use certain features of our services. If you choose to delete your data, you may not be able to use Crosswalk Wand as intended.</p>

    <h2>Contact Information:</h2>
    <p>For any questions or assistance regarding data deletion, please contact us at <a href="mailto:cw@kiloin.app">cw@kiloin.app</a>. Our support team is here to help you with any concerns you may have.</p>
</body>
